The three siblings who drowned last week at Mukinyai village in Molo, Nakuru County, were buried in the same grave at their parents' home on Friday.
Michael Kiritu (eight), Victor Kaniaru (11) and Grace Wairimu (15) attended Mukinyai Primary School. Michael was in Grade One, Victor in Grade Three and Grace Wairimu in Standard Six.



